subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/PublicDomain
object: no copyright; everything is permitted without restriction

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/License
object: a set of requests/permissions to users of a Work, e.g. a copyright license, the public domain, information for distributors

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/Attribution
object: credit be given to copyright holder and/or author

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/Requirement
object: an action that may or may not be requested of you

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/Distribution
object: distribution, public display, and publicly performance

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/Permission
object: an action that may or may not be allowed or desired

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/Agent
object: something (e.g. a person, corporation or computer) capable of creating things

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/Prohibition
object: something you may be asked not to do

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/SourceCode
object: source code (the preferred form for making modifications) must be provided for all derivative works

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/Notice
object: copyright and license notices be kept intact

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/DerivativeWorks
object: creation and distribution of derivative works

subject: http://web.resource.org/cc/ShareAlike
object: derivative works be licensed under the same terms as the original work
